The Duchess of Cambridge has undergone a style overhaul, swapping her midi dresses and A-line coats for separates and trousers. Royal expert Jennie Bond believes there is a very specific reason behind the style shift. Ms Bond told OK: "Kate is a practical princess and increasingly wears trousers to reflect that she's ready for business, whether that be kneeling down with kids or sliding down a slide." FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES...